# .scaffold/tables/patterns.table
# Design patterns in use → where → example → notes.
# AI generates code that FITS, not code that clashes.
#
# Format: PATTERN | WHERE_USED | EXAMPLE_FILE | NOTES

# Add your project's patterns below:
# Repository | Data layer | src/data/UserRepo.kt | All DB access through repos
# Factory | Object creation | src/core/Factory.kt | Complex init objects
# Observer | Events | src/events/Bus.kt | Prefer over callbacks
# Builder | Config | src/config/Builder.kt | Objects with >3 params
# Singleton | Globals | src/services/Analytics.kt | Use sparingly
